{"tid":1941365,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"向太炮轟林鄭防疫政策無能：港人的恥辱","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T15:49:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e52efd7bece26f082aef4a5530a7ef19fd19283","tid":1941365,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐全球，連日來香港確診個案激增，昨日港府宣佈新措施防疫，所有從台灣和澳門入境人士包括香港居民，同樣要接受強制檢疫，有關措施將為期14天。同時政府亦想推行「禁酒令」減少播毒風險，特首林鄭月娥昨日於記者會上，建議修例暫時禁止全港約8600家領有酒牌的食肆、酒吧等，停止售賣及供應酒品，減少社交接觸，避免人流聚集。<br />\n<br />\n措施引起外界不少爭議，向華強太太陳嵐也加入鬧特首無能，做成這樣也是香港人的恥辱，一向愛國的向太，平時都會支持政府，但今日她在微博炮轟林鄭。<br />\n<br />\n向太留言句句有骨講到出口，批評林鄭打爛港人飯碗：「香港特首無能，林鄭月娥我替你智商着急！你連每天去澳門上班的香港人都要隔離14天？那麼怎麼上班？妳是否有病啊？一萬多人將面臨失業，你知道嗎？你叫8600間有酒牌的餐廳不准賣酒？不是等於叫他們關門一樣？妳只是不想負責任補償！不好好管一管歐美返港戴手環的人不要亂跑出去玩？反而去弄些有的沒的規定！」<br />\n<br />\n向太又指一個沒有擔當的政府，難怪無論藍、黃色都討厭林鄭：「幾乎90%以上的人不喜歡你，也是奇葩了！做個地方特首做成這樣，也是香港人的恥辱。為甚麼人家澳門特首賀一誠先生才上任三個月，每次決策都令人鼓掌叫好呢？你學吓吧！不要學一半不學一半的。真是叫人着急！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFA5BX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFA5BX.jpg&h=818e715b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjLJu3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjLJu3D.jpg&h=3a2b6794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200324/3FYWK7JQ6GRLBAYX2HG3SPNAZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200324%2F3FYWK7JQ6GRLBAYX2HG3SPNAZM%2F&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ%2F2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=3693eb5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200324%2F3FYWK7JQ6GRLBAYX2HG3SPNAZM%2F&h=28239c44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200324/3FYWK7JQ6GRLBAYX2HG3SPNAZM/</a>"},{"pid":"e2ad65cc69cc0bc4232f626685c5a32edcc2d362","tid":1941365,"uid":52605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"講到尾原來又係擔心禁酒影響自己啲生意"},{"pid":"e83c6c0dd2baeed674a02287deb9ca80e7516e68","tid":1941365,"uid":211461,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"藍屍果然一燒到自己就即刻反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da89f33e9912499edfff841484a30776d2e0d09","tid":1941365,"uid":36378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"反面快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2bb2e6302c56a6ea2956515b3cb2ac6c88353e","tid":1941365,"uid":255926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"今次支持林鄭"},{"pid":"a66785c7fdbcc62b2c91addb31a08b90dc87ce7e","tid":1941365,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"carrie今次可以講返「官到無求膽自大」黎壓下場"},{"pid":"1057505afcac435ad059a54bcae84225ff7033fb","tid":1941365,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"林奠已成condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}